verbose_text: GFAP, a type II IF protein with various splice products where the GFAP-delta form is associated with neurogenic astrocytes is expressed in undifferentiated neurospheres (XREF_FIG B, C, H, I, K, L, red), as is the type II IF protein vimentin (XREF_FIG E, F, red).
